| archive-date = 2007-02-10
| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070210110952/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/h/heart_of_midlothian/6312529.stm
| dead-url = no
}}</ref>，2014–2017年擔任[[蘇格蘭足球超級聯賽|蘇格蘭足球超級聯賽]]球隊[[鄧迪足球俱樂部|鄧迪足球俱樂部]]的教練<ref name="dundee14">{{cite web|title=Dundee promotion 'good for Scottish football', says Paul Hartley|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/27272557|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=19 October 2014|date=4 May 2014|archive-date=2014-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140903082400/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/27272557|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他也曾25次代表[[蘇格蘭國家足球隊|蘇格蘭國家足球隊]]參賽。
